{"tid":1469882,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"你唔隱藏好自己身分 就拜託你唔好做前線亦唔好犯法","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:53:43.000Z","uid":4322,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa316f97633fa5a2f7b6ed7e30785a4aa009209","tid":1469882,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:25:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔好有僥倖心態 唔好做on9野 唔好有勇無謀 唔好咁易被人拉</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你唔隱藏好身份<br />\n周圍咁多cam咁多鏡頭 <br />\n琴晚仲要係機場<br />\n你淨係戴口罩咁打人係唔係搏拉先？<br />\n你話你唔矇面係咪on9先？<br />\n你隱藏好 話之你打到佢仆街打到佢死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔想有手足咁樣畀人拉呀 你麻包袋都唔會大庭廣眾喇</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n停一停 諗一諗呀各位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>你屌我分化又好鬼都好 我無所謂 我只想無人被捕流血</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"9afe1651cebcc0c455de68aff3d2a788586d4729","tid":1469882,"uid":95487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:26:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e171f5270b61ab8629b21bcece717e7a767019c","tid":1469882,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:30:07.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhhh"},{"pid":"88f046ce738e3e1bd89acac8647f6e6d271684ba","tid":1469882,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:37:40.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"9850e8b0510d4019dcbadb188d0a5a332dba81ca","tid":1469882,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:37:52.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"dc02ea522cc475aea8819bffa528dc8d127bd22e","tid":1469882,"uid":35364,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:40:59.000Z","msg":"捉到對家又唔想失威，<br />\n用幽默手法嘲諷羞辱就夠，<br />\n手持「平反六四」罰坐，<br />\n破壞證件、報名參軍之類。<br />\n顯得有文化又收威嚇之用。<br />\n<br />\n懲罰唔一定要流血，<br />\n有時只需要取其象徵意義。<br />\n檯底點懲治黑警都無所謂，<br />\n但檯面一定要好好睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n【反省與建議】「俘虜」處置提案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468537</a>"},{"pid":"7856a20d3d4763c2ea4c2ab9e5d79d2240e3c509","tid":1469882,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:41:47.000Z","msg":"手套都唔帶真係幫唔到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2996ccea7c70408351faf4670fff8dce1ca7117","tid":1469882,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7856a20d3d4763c2ea4c2ab9e5d79d2240e3c509","tid":1469882,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:41:47.000Z","msg":"手套都唔帶真係幫唔到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg